name: Mergulho Audiovisual Loop
description: A fragment from a collaboration between visual artist rollinos (@rollinos) and brazilian artist Jadsa (@jadsaaa). The 15 seconds loop is part of the visual work for 'Mergulho', track from "Olho de Vidro", Jadsa's breakthrough first record released by Balaclava Records, it contains a fragment from Jadsa's song as well. The work is commissioned by Music Video Festival (www.musicvideofestival.com.br).
